G686  
ἄρα  
ara  
*ar‘-ah*  
Probably from [142](g0142) (through the idea of *drawing* a conclusion.md);
a particle denoting an *inference* more or less decisive (as follows): -
haply, (what) manner (of man), no doubt, perhaps, so be, then,
therefore, truly, wherefore. Often used in connection with other
particles, especially [1065](g1065) or [3767](g3767) (after.md) or
[1487](g1487) (before). Compare also [687](g0687.md)  
